    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1KI 10:24" />¶ And all the <char style="w" strong="H0776">earth</char> <char style="w" strong="H1245">sought</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">to</char> <char style="w" strong="H8010">Solomon</char>, to <char style="w" strong="H8085">hear</char> his <char style="w" strong="H2451">wisdom</char>, which <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char> had <char style="w" strong="H5414">put</char> in his <char style="w" strong="H3820">heart</char>.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.24 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">sought to: Heb. sought the face of</char></note> <verse eid="1KI 10:24" /><verse number="25" style="v" sid="1KI 10:25" />And they <char style="w" strong="H0935">brought</char> every <char style="w" strong="H0376">man</char> his <char style="w" strong="H4503">present</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3627">vessels</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3701">silver</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H3627">vessels</char> of <char style="w" strong="H2091">gold</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H8008">garments</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H5402">armour</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H1314">spices</char>, <char style="w" strong="H5483">horses</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H6505">mules</char>, a <char style="w" strong="H1697">rate</char> <char style="w" strong="H8141">year</char> by <char style="w" strong="H8141">year</char>.<verse eid="1KI 10:25" /></para>
