    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1KI 12:1" />And <char style="w" strong="H7346">Rehoboam</char> <char style="w" strong="H3212">went</char> to <char style="w" strong="H7927">Shechem</char>: for all <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char> were <char style="w" strong="H0935">come</char> to <char style="w" strong="H7927">Shechem</char> to make him <char style="w" strong="H4427">king</char>. <verse eid="1KI 12:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1KI 12:2" />And it came to pass, when <char style="w" strong="H3379">Jeroboam</char> the <char style="w" strong="H1121">son</char> of <char style="w" strong="H5028">Nebat</char>, who was yet in <char style="w" strong="H4714">Egypt</char>, <char style="w" strong="H8085">heard</char> <char style="add">of it</char>, (for he was <char style="w" strong="H1272">fled</char> from the <char style="w" strong="H6440">presence</char> of <char style="w" strong="H4428">king</char> <char style="w" strong="H8010">Solomon</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H3379">Jeroboam</char> <char style="w" strong="H3427">dwelt</char> in <char style="w" strong="H4714">Egypt</char>;) <verse eid="1KI 12:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1KI 12:3" />That they <char style="w" strong="H7971">sent</char> and <char style="w" strong="H7121">called</char> him. And <char style="w" strong="H3379">Jeroboam</char> and all the <char style="w" strong="H6951">congregation</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char> <char style="w" strong="H0935">came</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H1696">spake</char> unto <char style="w" strong="H7346">Rehoboam</char>, <char style="w" strong="H0559">saying</char>, <verse eid="1KI 12:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1KI 12:4" />Thy <char style="w" strong="H0001">father</char> <char style="w" strong="H7185">made</char> our <char style="w" strong="H5923">yoke</char> <char style="w" strong="H7185">grievous</char>: now therefore make thou the <char style="w" strong="H7186">grievous</char> <char style="w" stron