  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1KI 13:20" />¶ And it came to pass, as they <char style="w" strong="H3427">sat</char> at the <char style="w" strong="H7979">table</char>, that the <char style="w" strong="H1697">word</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> came unto the <char style="w" strong="H5030">prophet</char> that brought him <char style="w" strong="H7725">back</char>: <verse eid="1KI 13:20" /><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1KI 13:21" />And he <char style="w" strong="H7121">cried</char> unto the <char style="w" strong="H0376">man</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char> that <char style="w" strong="H0935">came</char> from <char style="w" strong="H3063">Judah</char>, <char style="w" strong="H0559">saying</char>, Thus <char style="w" strong="H0559">saith</char> the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>, Forasmuch <char style="w" strong="H3282">as</char> thou hast <char style="w" strong="H4784">disobeyed</char> the <char style="w" strong="H6310">mouth</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>, and hast not <char style="w" strong="H8104">kept</char> the <char style="w" strong="H4687">commandment</char> which the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> thy <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char> <char style="w" strong="H6680">commanded</char> thee, <verse eid="1KI 13:21" /><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1KI 13:22" />But camest <char style="w" strong="H7725">back</char>, and hast <char style="w" strong="H0398">eaten</char> <char style="w" strong="H3899">bread</char> and <char style="w" strong="H8354">drunk</char> <char style="w" strong="H4325">water</char> in the <char style="w" strong="H4725">place</char>, of the which <char style="add">the <char style="nd">Lord</char></char> did <char style="w" strong="H1696">say</char> to thee, <char style="w" strong="H0398">Eat</char> no <char style="w" strong="H3899">brea