    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1KI 22:1" />And they <char style="w" strong="H3427">continued</char> <char style="w" strong="H7969">three</char> <char style="w" strong="H8141">years</char> without <char style="w" strong="H4421">war</char> between <char style="w" strong="H0758">Syria</char> and <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char>. <verse eid="1KI 22:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1KI 22:2" />And it came to pass in the <char style="w" strong="H7992">third</char> <char style="w" strong="H8141">year</char>, that <char style="w" strong="H3092">Jehoshaphat</char> the <char style="w" strong="H4428">king</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3063">Judah</char> came <char style="w" strong="H3381">down</char> to the <char style="w" strong="H4428">king</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char>. <verse eid="1KI 22:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1KI 22:3" />And the <char style="w" strong="H4428">king</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char> <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char> unto his <char style="w" strong="H5650">servants</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3045">Know</char> ye that <char style="w" strong="H7433">Ramoth</char> in <char style="w" strong="H1568">Gilead</char> <char style="add">is</char> ours, and we <char style="add">be</char> <char style="w" strong="H2814">still</char>, <char style="add">and</char> <char style="w" strong="H3947">take</char> it not out of the <char style="w" strong="H3027">hand</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H4428">king</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0758">Syria</char>?<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">22.3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">still…: Heb. silent from taking it</char></note> <verse eid="1KI 22:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1KI 22:4" />And he <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char> unto <char style="w" strong="H3092">Jehoshaphat</char>, Wilt thou <char style="w" strong="H3212">go</char> with me to <char style="w" strong="H4421